 court the jerusalem post  july  retrieved  august    azulay moran  july  netanyahu i approved the boycott law ynetnews retrieved  august    australian lawmakers support israeli business jewish telegraphic agency  july  retrieved  august    kerr christian  july  support for boycotts on israel backfired the australian retrieved  july    julia gillard denounces activists as antiisrael protest turns antisemitic  higgins ean  may  in a democracy freedom of expression had to allow a capacity for dissent the australian retrieved  may    ghnassia michaël  march  boycotter les produits disraël  non ce nest pas de la liberté dexpression le nouvel observateur retrieved  july    tribunal slams academic for bringing antisemitism case the times higher education  march   government suffers defeat in court by palestine campaigners over boycott divestment and sanctions palestine solidarity campaign june   wikisource has original text related to this article palestinian civil society calls for boycott divestment and sanctions against israel retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleboycottsofisraeloldid categories boycotts of israelzionismhuman rights in israelhuman rights in the palestinian territorieshidden categories wikipedia articles incorporating text from the congressional research servicewebarchive template wayback linksall articles with dead external linksarticles with dead external links from july articles with permanently dead external linksarticles with dead external links from november pages containing links to subscriptiononly contentcs frenchlanguage sources frarticles with dead external links from november cs norwegianlanguage sources nocs uses hebrewlanguage script hecs hebrewlanguage sources hewikipedia pages under  editing restrictionarticles needing additional references from november all articles needing additional referencesarticles lacking reliable references from november all articles lacking reliable referencesuse dmy dates from november all articles w