ica israel investments danya cebus reuters oslo wed  august   a b norways sovereign wealth fund joins exodus from israel financial times  february subscription required  german company pulls out of israel rail project because it cuts through west bank the washington post associated press  may   caterpillar cut from social index over israel al jazeera  june   israel divestiture spurs clash jewish leaders condemn move by presbyterian church by alan cooperman washington post page a  september   kaleem jaweed  july  presbyterians reject divestment related to israelipalestinian conflict the huffington post retrieved  july    presbyterians vote to divest holdings to pressure israel the new york times  june   new zealand superannuation fund excludes three companies on responsible investment grounds new zealand superannuation fund  december   ravid barak  february  denmarks largest bank blacklists israels hapoalim over settlement construction haaretz   israels sodastream leaves west bank financial times  september  sodastream the israeli maker of home fizzy drink dispensers will next week cease production at its factory near the west bank settlement of maale adumim after being pressured by campaigners around the world for doing business on occupied palestinian landsubscription required  benjamin joffewalt  may  lecturers back boycott of israeli academics the guardian london   traubmann tamara  june  british academic boycott expires after teaching unions merge haaretz   spain contest bans israeli team affiliated with west bank college haaretz associated press  december  retrieved  december    ntnu says no to academic boycott of israel press release norwegian university of science and technology  november   ahren raphael  january  for first time us professors call for academic and cultural boycott of israel haaretz   over  academics endorse boycott of israel arab news wvns  september    university of johannesburg votes to sever ties with bgu the jerusalem post  march   kalman