ould make it hard to divide jerusalem israel jta  july    the legislation would require a knesset supermajority to approve the handover of land in israels capital including for peace read more page  of  take action now follow usfanslikefollowersfollowfollowersfollow subscribe to our newsletter now editor picks tchaikovsky’s jewish problem culture july   adl condemns sermons by california imams that called for destruction of religion july   how tisha b’av can help us understand the refugee experience middle east july   popular posts  jewish inventions that changed the world blog february    jewish inventions that changed the world blog july   jspace quotables  memorable quotes about the holocaust blog january   popular categorycurrent eventsisraelunited statesblogworldeuropepoliticsentertainmentjudaism about usjspace news is one of the fastest growing online jewish newspapers founded in  to document news on israel the middle east and jewish world at large it was established to provide a single source where the entire jewish and israeli community could come together in conversationfollow us about advertise with us terms and conditions privacy policy help find us on google  copyright   jewish world alliance all rights reserved wowmodalwindows id bank of israel  exchange rates home credit data sharing about the bank of israel contact us العربيةעברית bank of israel consumer information publications monetary policy markets research data  statistics banking supervision payment systems currency education markets librariesmonetary toolsreserve requirementexchange ratesforeign currency marketforeign exchange reserves reportpress releasesclarificationsdatamonetary policy circularsthe telbor market mailing lists representative exchange rates currency and period currency and exchange rate rates of change foreign currency conversion other currency exchange rates dates search print latest update  currency unit country rate nis daily change graph dollar  usa   pound  great britain 